{"name": "oceana-token", "metadata": {"name": "oceana-token", "version": "0.0.4", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["build", "setuptools", "wheel", "requests", "python-decouple", "typing-extensions", "requests-mock", "pyjwt", "pytest", "coverage", "flake8"], "summary": "Oceana API library to manage authentication token and headers", "upload_time": 1733164033}, "documentation": ["# oceana_token\nOceana API library to manage authentication token and headers\n\n\n## Setup\n\nInstall latest version\n```shell\npip install oceana_token\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nCreate authentication headers:\n```python\nfrom oceana_token import *\nimport json\n\n# Authentication in Oceana API\noceana_api_client = Authenticate(url=\"http://127.0.0.1:5000\",\n                                 client_id=\"oceana-api-client\",\n                                 client_secret=\"bad_password\")\ntoken = oceana_api_client.get_token()\n\n# Create headers\nheaders = oceana_api_client.headers(headers={})\n\n# Add authentication header\nheaders = oceana_api_client.authorization_header(headers={})\n\n# Create headers from template\nheaders = json.loads(oceana_api_auth_header.format(token=oceana_api_client.get_token()))\n```\n\nRequest an endpoint:\n```python\nimport requests\n\nheaders = ...\n\nresponse = requests.get(url=\"http://127.0.0.1:5000/v1/organization/id/1\", headers=headers, verify=False)\n```\n\n## Environment\n\nProperties in environment variables:\n```shell\n# Example\nOCEANA_API_URL=\"http://127.0.0.1:5000\"\nOCEANA_API_CLIENT_ID=\"oceana-api-client\"\nOCEANA_API_CLIENT_SECRET=\"bad_password\"\nOCEANA_API_LOGGER_LEVEL=\"DEBUG\"\nOCEANA_API_LOGGER_FORMAT=\"%(asctime)s - [%(name)-25s] - %(levelname)-5s - %(message)s\"\n```\n\n## Packaging\n\nBuild package\n```shell\n# Using build package\npython -m build\n```\n\n\nRun tests\n```shell\n# All tests\npytest -q -rP\n\n# Partial tests\npytest tests/unit/test_authentication.py -v -rP\npytest tests/unit/test_header.py -v -rP\npytest tests/unit/test_jwt.py -v -rP\n```\n\n```shell\n# Reinstall avoiding reinstalling dependencies\npip install --upgrade --no-deps --force-reinstall dist\\oceana_token-0.0.4-py3-none-any.whl\n```\n\n```shell\n# Reinstall with dependencies\npip install dist\\oceana_token-0.0.4-py3-none-any.whl --force-reinstall\n```\n\nCheck style guide enforcement\n```shell\nflake8 . --count --exit-zero --max-complexity=10 --max-line-length=127 --statistics\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Library                | Version |\n|------------------------|---------|\n| build                  | 1.2.1   |\n| setuptools             | 67.8.0  |\n| wheel                  | 0.38.4  |\n| requests               | 2.29.0  |\n| pytest                 | 7.4.0   |\n| coverage               | 6.4.4   |\n| flake8                 | 4.0.1   |\n| python-decouple        | 3.8     |\n| typing-extensions      | 4.12.2  |\n\n\n## Releases\n**Version 0.0.4**:\n   - Added configurable API version\n**Version 0.0.3**:\n   - First version\n"], "modules": [{"name": "oceana_token.utils", "documentation": ["coding: utf-8"], "functions": [{"name": "oceana_token.utils.string_base64", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "s", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "oceana_token.utils.base64_string", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "b", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "oceana_token.exceptions", "documentation": ["coding: utf-8"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "oceana_token.exceptions.OceanaError", "bases": ["Exception"], "methods": [{"name": "oceana_token.exceptions.OceanaError.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, 